videos.description: Donta Hall puts Alabama on the board quickly with a dunk, drawing a foul in the process.
videos.headline: Hall dunks and draws foul

videos.description: Tevin Mack delivers a deep 3-pointer to give Alabama a 32-29 lead over Kentucky.
videos.headline: Alabama takes lead on long 3

videos.description: Ashton Hagans brings Kentucky within 1 of Alabama when he picks up a basket and the foul.
videos.headline: Hagans drives to basket and draws foul

videos.description: Kira Lewis Jr. rebounds the ball on a missed shot by Kentucky and passes to Herbert Jones, who finishes with a dunk.
videos.headline: Alabama capitalizes on Kentucky miss with dunk

videos.description: Kentucky almost loses the ball to Alabama, but they get it back to Keldon Johnson, who passes to PJ Washington for a dunk.
videos.headline: Johnson fights off defenders, Washington finishes with dunk

videos.description: Tyler Herro misses a 3-pointer at the buzzer as Alabama upsets Kentucky 77-75.
videos.headline: Alabama wins after Kentucky misses 3 at buzzer
